the delivery predates the sweep by more than MAX_ARM_LOOKBACK_MS (2h), so a
25h-stale cold arm no longer breaches on the first sweep. This pre-existing
AC5 admin test relied on a 24h-stale delivery still breaching; retune the
delivery to sit inside the 2h horizon but past the 30m deadline so it remains
a legitimate breach and still exposes a ladder rung.

