From 96b84ce54a7d107be96f15f08a0ed3f9810420f9 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: "Igor (Back End Dev)" <igor@fancyfleet.dev>
Date: Mon, 13 Jul 2026 01:26:06 -0600
Subject: [PATCH 9/9] =?UTF-8?q?AI-2178:=20dispatch=20circuit=20breaker=20?=
 =?UTF-8?q?=E2=80=94=20stop=20re-waking=20a=20delegate=20on=20a=20stuck=20?=
